item.title: CVE-2020-9058|2024-08-04T10:19:19.970Z -- dome -- dm501
item.description: Z-Wave devices based on Silicon Labs 500 series chipsets using CRC-16 encapsulation, including but likely not limited to the Linear LB60Z-1 version 3.5, Dome DM501 version 4.26, and Jasco ZW4201 version 4.05, do not implement encryption or replay protection.
